The paper discusses a framework for analyzing large amounts of data produced by devices in data centers. This falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of statistical analysis and machine learning techniques, which could fall under the categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.LG).
